graph LR
    ModelRegistryOp[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|database backend| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|database backend| MySQL[MySQL 5.7+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio Service Mesh 1.20+]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|external auth| Authorino[Authorino 0.17+]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|certificate mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|service mesh control plane| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|potential UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|container images| Images[Model Registry Images]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|orchestration| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    ModelRegistryOp -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Deployed Service Dependencies
    subgraph "Deployed by Operator"
        Registry[Model Registry Service]
    end

    Registry -->|uses| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|uses| MySQL
    Registry -.->|mTLS| Istio
    Registry -.->|auth/authz| Authorino
    Registry -->|SubjectAccessReview| K8sAPI

    %% Image Details
    Images -->|REST API| RestImage[quay.io/opendatahub/<br/>model-registry:latest]
    Images -->|gRPC API| GrpcImage[quay.io/opendatahub/<br/>mlmd-grpc-server:latest]

